### Dylan5797
## About Me
I'm your average volleyball and soccer playing trigonometry art loving low poly enthusiast math wizz 12 year old programmer genius. I mainly use Python, Scratch and JavaScript and I'm pretty sure I'm wasting my other programming skills. I am [Dylan5797](http://scratch.mit.edu/users/Dylan5797) on [Scratch](http://scratch.mit.edu/). I edit the [Scratch Wiki](http://wiki.scratch.mit.edu/) (of course I joined, I'm a grammar and politically correct freak.) As I said in my sarcastic sum of me in one sentence, I love trig and low poly art. I enjoy volleyball and soccer, and I love math, unlike the average student :stuck_out_tongue:.
## About This Website
Here, I have some of my projects in Python, mostly Scratch related.
